The Women in STEM newsletters are a product of the Tandon School of Engineerings initiative to promote women in STEM and related fields. The newsletter was first published in 2015. It includes event and program listings, application deadlines, awards, club information, history spotlights, faculty updates, and mentorship opportunities.
